      "description": "Initial release of Deck — draggable widget-grid dashboards for Obsidian.\n\n**Highlights**\n- Structured task model (parse/serialize)\n- AI session registry + session list modal for AI delegation\n- Two-way Google Sheets sync (adapter + auto-sync watcher)\n- Home dashboard template\n- Gantt / Kanban widget updates\n- Existing widgets: Dataview, Bases, notes, calendar, Gmail mail viewer\n\n**Install (manual):** copy `main.js`, `manifest.json`, `styles.css` into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/deck-dashboard/`.",
